snippet.title: Everyone Knows Christopher Columbus Was a B*tch: Week In Review | The Amber Ruffin
snippet.description:
The Amber Ruffin Show. New Episodes Streaming Every Friday on Peacock: https://pck.tv/3pOiao8

Reserve your spot in the live studio audience for The Amber Ruffin Show at https://1iota.com/show/1210/the-amber-ruffin-show

Columbus Day was this week, and it’s crazy we still celebrate this man, because everyone knows… Columbus was a b*tch! 

 #TheAmberRuffinShow #PeacockTV #WeekInReview

Show Synopsis: Amber showcases her signature smart-and-silly take on the news of the week, responding to it all with a charming, late-night mix of seriousness, nonsense, and evening gowns.
